Throws unless `msg.sender` is the current owner, an authorized operator, or the approved address for this NFT. Throws if `_from` is not the current owner. Throws if `_to` is the zero address. Throws if `_tokenId` is not a valid NFT. When transfer is complete, this function checks if `_to` is a smart contract (code size > 0).
